1159
00:41:35,893 --> 00:41:37,294
Try some, Min-jung.

1160
00:41:37,361 --> 00:41:39,096
It must be a shame to eat it alone.

1161
00:41:39,163 --> 00:41:40,564
I didn't touch this part.

1162
00:41:40,631 --> 00:41:42,433
He's still in his right mind.

1163
00:41:42,500 --> 00:41:43,767
Give me just one bite.

1164
00:41:43,834 --> 00:41:44,668
HEHE

1165
00:41:44,735 --> 00:41:46,303
-And the veggies.
-It smells so good.

1166
00:41:46,370 --> 00:41:48,305
-It's really good.
-Is it?

1167
00:41:48,372 --> 00:41:52,276
-It'd be even better in his office.
-I'm sure.

1168
00:41:52,343 --> 00:41:54,411
-He's enjoying it very much.
-He is.

1169
00:41:54,478 --> 00:41:56,146
