1170
00:41:56,213 --> 00:41:57,948
He makes it look so good.

1171
00:41:59,149 --> 00:42:01,385
It's really good. I mean it.

1172
00:42:01,452 --> 00:42:02,887
I'm serious. Wow.

1173
00:42:02,953 --> 00:42:04,688
Does it taste like lasagna?

1174
00:42:04,755 --> 00:42:07,024
-Totally lasagna.
-I see.

1175
00:42:07,091 --> 00:42:08,626
That's amazing.

1176
00:42:08,692 --> 00:42:10,628
It's seriously I-sagna, lasagna.

1177
00:42:11,529 --> 00:42:12,630
I-sagna.

1178
00:42:12,696 --> 00:42:15,266
-This is incredible.
-"It's incredible."

1179
00:42:15,332 --> 00:42:17,635
ANOTHER BITE

1180
00:42:18,269 --> 00:42:20,471
-It's so incredible.
-He really did it.

1181
00:42:20,538 --> 00:42:22,973
I'm sure he'll receive a good grade.

1182
00:42:23,040 --> 00:42:25,943
Next, Chef Sung-jun's dish.

