00:42:26,010 --> 00:42:29,113
VONGOLE RISOTTO

1184
00:42:29,179 --> 00:42:32,750
ADORNED WITH A SEAFOOD-VEGGIE WREATH

1185
00:42:33,284 --> 00:42:37,521
A KICK OF KIMCHI PESTO ON TOP

1186
00:42:38,022 --> 00:42:41,759
