CHOI HYUN-SUK'S GONE, FINE SPRING DAY

1187
00:42:42,326 --> 00:42:43,460
-Wow.
-It's so pretty.

1188
00:42:43,527 --> 00:42:48,499
Chef Sung-jun made vongole risotto.

1189
00:42:48,566 --> 00:42:50,701
