1190
00:42:50,768 --> 00:42:51,602
When were you born?

1191
00:42:51,669 --> 00:42:53,003
-In '95.
-In '95.

1192
00:42:53,070 --> 00:42:54,171
In '95?

1193
00:42:56,106 --> 00:42:58,208
