1196
00:43:01,645 --> 00:43:02,580
Life must've been rough.

1197
00:43:02,646 --> 00:43:04,615
-He went to college in '95.
-In '95.

1198
00:43:04,682 --> 00:43:06,984
-He did.
-Are you serious?

1199
00:43:07,051 --> 00:43:08,619
He was born in 1995.

1200
00:43:08,852 --> 00:43:10,487
TRULY LIKE A PROFESSOR AND HIS STUDENT

1201
00:43:10,554 --> 00:43:14,391
Cooked by the chef who was born
